data.description: Brick Ranch on 3.67 acres! Vintage 1962, cedar walls & ceilings in the living room, kitchen, and family room. 2 Skylights. Full unfinished basement. The home has not been updated since the 70's this will need remodeling. Original bathrooms you know the pink tile. 70's kitchen. The garage was enclosed into a family room. The back porch can be enclosed or returned to a screened porch. One outbuilding with a concrete floor needs a roof repair. Parts of the property were fenced for goats at one time. Not many interior photos due to packing and moving. Conventional and Cash only.
